356
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:03,880
It also offers operation simulations.

357
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:05,840
I’ve heard of it before.

358
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,400
Such a system

359
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,440
