541
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,000
Hello, Mi Ka?

542
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:50,080
What’s up?

543
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:52,480
Why is here a hanging steam iron?

544
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:54,320
Well,

545
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:55,720
